<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-53EFAC8C-E032-471D-A8A5-555FEAB34F28" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-53EFAC8C-E032-471D-A8A5-555FEAB34F28" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">White dark lines from left to right</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-50B00AD6-0A38-41AB-B3CF-DCE2951AFA8A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/><table id="GUID-53E5F599-B620-44AD-919D-C7253ABD770C" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-05CC759C-78C7-4362-9256-3E8EE5049CCB" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-42C477D1-2C42-4C49-9921-D7F891C796AF-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-42C477D1-2C42-4C49-9921-D7F891C796AF-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E2A086B7-D4F1-48C2-A4C5-3982C68B632B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FDEB03EF-8BAF-4C99-B7DF-725889D96B65-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FDEB03EF-8BAF-4C99-B7DF-725889D96B65-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Dark and white lines are visible in the carriage direction. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Optical density of the lines differs from left to right. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Lines are visible at the edges of the print. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Lines appear in all colors simultaneously. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> One line per media step/swath visible 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The lines have equal distances and is depended on the print mode 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> In most cases the lines disappear during printing. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> If this issue continues after several meters follow 
<xref keyref="PQ_02" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-96B3FD5F-826E-4464-B3E5-968ED22A262E.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text Image position slowly drifting / Winding not correct?>Image position slowly drifting / Winding not correct</xref> 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "/> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-31B6BCBA-97B3-4EFF-B9D7-1A7EFCD054B3" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Functional Logging (if available)</title><fig id="GUID-15498449-A032-4DCA-B871-09538193E977" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">Media step accuracy</title><image href="GUID-B5099A94-D1CA-41C0-81CB-FBB331447A88-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B5099A94-D1CA-41C0-81CB-FBB331447A88-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">As can be seen the media step error is different between the left and right side (Blue and Orange lines). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">A big difference between the orange and the blue lines in typical for the artifact described in this chapter. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Buffer plate</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In most cases this difference can also be seen in the performance of the buffer plate (see below). 
</p><fig id="GUID-2A67B729-D42F-4AAE-B368-505A809EF2C5" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title ">buffer plate</title><image href="GUID-7BA64318-FFD8-43F1-B3A3-FF3CDF3B9A11-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7BA64318-FFD8-43F1-B3A3-FF3CDF3B9A11-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">As can be seen the position of the buffer plate is different between the left and right side in the first half of the print. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">During printing this difference is slowly corrected. This behavior is typical for wrongly loaded media in the drawer. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-B49466B8-DB07-4B4C-8E98-C235D715DD91" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">ADAM-triggers</title><p class="- topic/p ">In case the buffer plate is not working well, 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">15-T-001 Buffer verification required</b> is present in ADAM 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-5C344431-E4B3-42DC-A38D-58AB6C973C65" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-350E7B69-8713-48A4-B20D-19B049674A59-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-350E7B69-8713-48A4-B20D-19B049674A59-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
